headline: One Sector the Ruling Won’t Affect: Defense
summary: Don’t expect defense stocks to move much on Friday’s ruling by the Supreme Court that President Donald Trump’s Liberation Day tariffs are illegal.  Defense companies' supply chains are mostly domestic.  Tariffs rarely come up on defense contractors’ conference calls.
